text: Natia Danelia (; born 23 September 2003) is a Georgian footballer who plays as a midfielder for FC Nike Tbilisi and the Georgia women's national team. ==Career== Danelia has been capped for the Georgia national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== Category:2003 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:Women's footballers from Georgia (country) Category:Georgia (country) women's international footballers
